# Dev-only artifacts — kept locally for skill-creator regression testing,
# excluded from GitHub and from the bundled .plugin zip. Eval prompts may
# reference real workflow names (people, projects); workspaces/ holds
# historical iteration outputs which bloat the public repo without giving
# downstream users anything actionable.
plugins/process-design/skills/process-design/evals/
workspaces/

